trans-unit.source:
\n

Defines a generalized type-specific comparison method that a value type or class implements to order or sort its instances.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxx x xxxxxxxxxxx xxxx$xxxxxxxx xxxxxxxxxx xxxxxx xxxx x xxxxx xxxx xx xxxxx xxxxxxxxxx xx xxxxx xx xxxx xxx xxxxxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

Compares the current instance with another object of the same type and returns an integer that indicates whether the current instance precedes, follows, or occurs in the same position in the sort order as the other object.

\n
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxx xxxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxx xxx xxxxxxx xx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxx xxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx$ xxxxxxx$ xx xxxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxxxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxxx xx xxx xxxxx xxxxxx.$$x$$x

trans-unit.source:
\n

An object to compare with this instance.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$Xx xxxxxx xx xxxxxxx xxxx xxxx xxxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

A value that indicates the relative order of the objects being compared.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$X xxxxx xxxx xxxxxxxxx xxx xxxxxxxx xxxxx xx xxx xxxxxxx xxxxx xxxxxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
The return value has these meanings:

Value

Meaning

Less than zero

This instance precedes obj in the sort order.
trans-unit.target: Xxx xxxxxx xxxxx xxx xxxxx xxxxxxxx$ $$x$$x$x$Xxxxx $$x$$x$x$Xxxxxxx $$x$$x$xxxxx$$xxxxx$$xx$$xx$$x$x$Xxxx xxxx xxxx $$x$$x$$xx$$xx$$x$x$Xxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxxxxx $xx$xxx$$xx$ xx xxx xxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
Zero

This instance occurs in the same position in the sort order as obj.
trans-unit.target: $$x$$x$$xx$$$xx$$xx$$xx$$x$x$Xxxx $$x$$x$$xx$$xx$$x$x$Xxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxxxxxx xx xxx xxxx xxxxx xx $xx$xxx$$xx$.

trans-unit.source:
Greater than zero

This instance follows obj in the sort order.
trans-unit.target: $$x$$x$$xx$$$xx$$xx$$xx$$x$x$Xxxxxxx xxxx xxxx $$x$$x$$xx$$xx$$x$x$Xxxx xxxxxxxx xxxxxxx $xx$xxx$$xx$ xx xxx xxxx xxxxx.

trans-unit.source:
\n

\nobj is not the same type as this instance.
trans-unit.target: $x$x$$x$xx$xxx$$xx$ xx xxx xxx xxxx xxxx xx xxxx xxxxxxxx.
